{"id":207694,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/01/外媒-中国拒绝军队国家化/","date":"2012-01-31T06:53:32Z","modified":"2012-01-31T06:53:32Z","title":"外媒: 中国拒绝军队国家化","content":"<p><a name=\"more\"></a></p>\n<div>\n<span></span></div>\n<div>\n<span></span></div>\n<div>\n<span>中国军队报纸《解放军报》<span>1</span><span>月</span><span>29</span><span>日强调，中国共产党对迅速现代化的中国军队拥有最终控制权。</span></span><span></span></div>\n<div>\n<span></span></div>\n<div>\n<span>经中央军委批准，《解放军报》发表了《中央军委关于大力发展先进军事文化的意见》，号召中国<span>230</span><span>万人的解放军发展先进的军事文化，并提出，坚持把培育当代革命军人核心价值观作为发展先进军事文化的根本任务。</span></span><span></span></div>\n<div>\n<span>同时，作为执政党的共产党将在巩固这一社会主义意识形态上起领导作用。</span><span></span></div>\n<div>\n<span></span></div>\n<div>\n<span>外电评价，这一呼吁与中国军队国家化的发展方向背道而驰，表明了解放军在加强装备和战斗力的同时，执政党将继续控制军队的政策。<span>VOA</span></span><span></span></div>\n<div><img alt=\"\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/3112334774117141878-1836675393779835967?l=www.molihua.org\" width=\"1\" /></div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/QBG13r-XKgfFeaT1sCKTBV8Qri8/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap=\"ismap\" src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/QBG13r-XKgfFeaT1sCKTBV8Qri8/0/di\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/QBG13r-XKgfFeaT1sCKTBV8Qri8/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap=\"ismap\" src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/QBG13r-XKgfFeaT1sCKTBV8Qri8/1/di\" /></a></p>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/molihua/QiRF/~4/mbzyvcpx1aM\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://docs.google.com/a/chinadigitaltimes.net/spreadsheet/embeddedform?hl=zh-CN&#038;formkey=dGlaNkplWEluYV9TWUxDQkhfaDlxQmc6MQ\" width=\"510\" height=\"334\" frameborder=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\">Loading&#8230;</iframe></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=738338\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAI